_sText: Hey guys!Elevator battle is a map that i thought it would be realy fun to play so i made it!basicly you get started in the elevator with a gun and shoot the other team from the other side as both elevators move down!Hope you enjoy what i made and thanks if you download!NOTE:ive tested the map it works fine online with others but the only problem is it dosnt work with bots..i will fix that also in the next release!BTW just unrar the map where cstrike folder is and everything is done;)
